ahankaar se chaaya andhkaar
punya paap ka hisaab main karu ni
ye chausar ka khel chaape paise chaar
lunga sab main cheen jaise shakuni
karu ni, inke jaise kaam
wo bhi sareaam
jo ye khud ki hi chaate
aur bane bade fanne khan
aur yahi bane shaktimaan
ye gangadhar se launde chode sirf ye baatein
hiranyakashyap wali harkatein
to banu Narsimha aur karu narsanghaar
ye tera ahankaar kisi kaam ka ni
das hain sar aur chode das ye baatein jaise
raavan main vaman tu raja bali bane bali ka bakra
seedha hi chalra ye paon tere sar par
bina sar pair ki baat yaha kar mat
